15:55.801 --> 15:57.367
Come On.

15:59.067 --> 16:00.067
Cough It Up.

16:05.067 --> 16:06.300
Oh, Hey.

16:06.300 --> 16:08.200
Let Me Help You
With That, Henry.

16:08.200 --> 16:11.167
What Service.

16:11.167 --> 16:14.601
You'd Make An Excellent
Valet Or Squire.

16:14.601 --> 16:17.334
Henry, Maybe Next Time

16:17.334 --> 16:20.133
We Should Try And Recycle
Your Wine Bottles.

16:20.133 --> 16:21.133
Why?

