Recycling Is
The Most Insidious Idea

16:23.434 --> 16:24.567
Of This Generation.

16:24.567 --> 16:26.067
That And Helping
The Homeless,

16:26.067 --> 16:27.934
 <I>Most Of Whom Deserve</I>
 <I>The Position.</I>

16:27.934 --> 16:31.567
What The Government Should
Really Focus On Is Sex.

16:31.567 --> 16:33.667
 <I>If We Could</I>
 <I>Control That,</I>

16:33.667 --> 16:36.000
We Could Solve Anything.

16:36.000 --> 16:37.367
So You See Sex

16:37.367 --> 16:39.901
As The Cause Of All
Of Society's Problems?

16:39.901 --> 16:42.868
Absolutely.
You'll Find I'm
To The Right Of The Pope

16:42.868 --> 16:44.701
On Most Of These Issues.

16:44.701 --> 16:46.501
Well, Anyway,

16:46.501 --> 16:48.067
If I May Change
The Subject,

16:48.067 --> 16:51.234
You Look Very Nice.
Are You Going Out Somewhere?

16:51.234 --> 16:53.133
Yes, I'm Seeing

16:53.133 --> 16:56.033
The Billionairess
Vivian Cudlip This Evening.

16:56.033 --> 16:59.234
She Phoned Me
About An Event
Only 10 Minutes Ago,

16:59.234 --> 17:01.968
But The Queen
Must Be Obeyed.

17:01.968 --> 17:05.032
- Wow, A Billionairess.
- Mmm.

17:05.032 --> 17:07.701
And To Think
A Lowly Fellow Like Me

17:07.701 --> 17:09.800
Was About To Treat You
To Dinner.

17:09.800 --> 17:12.934
I Had A Banner Day.
I Even Got A Job.

17:12.934 --> 17:14.467
Congratulations!

17:14.467 --> 17:17.334
I Knew You Were A Man
Who Could Pay The Rent.

17:17.334 --> 17:18.968
What Type Of Position?

17:18.968 --> 17:20.834
- It's At A Magazine.
- Mmm.

17:20.834 --> 17:22.934
An Environmental Journal.

17:22.934 --> 17:25.233
