18:57.701 --> 18:59.868
Don't Be Such A Milquetoast.
As Napoleon Said,

18:59.868 --> 19:01.167
- "If Rape Is Imminent..."
- Henry!

19:01.167 --> 19:03.834
- "...Relax And Enjoy It!"
- Woman: <I>Asshole!</I>

19:03.834 --> 19:06.234
All Right,
Here's How It's Done.

19:06.234 --> 19:07.868
The Intermission Is
About To Begin.

19:07.868 --> 19:09.534
So When You See Somebody
Coming Out,

19:09.534 --> 19:11.868
You Simply Say,
"Oh, Are You Leaving So Soon?

19:11.868 --> 19:13.334
Well, If You Are,

19:13.334 --> 19:16.334
May I Have Your Ticket
And Your Re-Entry Stub?"

19:16.334 --> 19:19.033
Now, You Have
To Get The Re-Entry Stub.
That's Very Important.

19:19.033 --> 19:20.667
Without It,
The Ticket Is Useless.

19:20.667 --> 19:22.200
- Do You Understand?
- I Think So.

19:24.267 --> 19:26.901
Henry, Henry!
I Got Two Tickets!

19:26.901 --> 19:29.467
Shh, Shh.
And The Re-Entry Stubs?

19:29.467 --> 19:31.100
Well, One Stub,
But I Think--

19:31.100 --> 19:34.100
Didn't I Tell You
It Was Crucial To Get
The Re-Entry Stub?

19:34.100 --> 19:35.801
Which Part Of That
Didn't You Understand?

19:35.801 --> 19:38.534
She Only Took One.
Why Are You Yelling At Me?!

19:38.534 --> 19:40.200
- You Didn't Get Anything.
- That's Irrelevant.

19:40.200 --> 19:41.968
The Point Is
Without The Re-Entry Stub

19:41.968 --> 19:43.734
The Ticket Is Useless.

19:43.734 --> 19:46.033
- <I>( MUSICAL TONES PLAY )</I>
- Show Time, Darling.

19:46.033 --> 19:49.400
Oh Dear. Well,
We're Going To Have
To Try To Sneak In.

19:49.400 --> 19:50.534
All Right.

19:53.300 --> 19:55.334
Here's A Program.
That Will Help.

19:55.334 --> 19:57.200
You Go First,
I'll Be Behind You.

19:57.200 --> 19:58.734
I'll Be Senile,
You'll Be Angry.

19:58.734 --> 20:00.100
We'll Bluff
Our Way In. Go.

20:01.501 --> 20:04.033
( SINGING )

20:06.968 --> 20:10.067
Where Is--
Where's My Re-Entry Stub?
I Had It.

20:10.067 --> 20:12.667
Did You Take It?
I Hand It To You?

20:12.667 --> 20:14.667
- No.
- I Must Have Handed
It To You.

20:14.667 --> 20:16.400
No, You Didn't,
Father!

20:16.400 --> 20:19.367
For Heaven's Sake,
Try To Remember Where
You Put Things!

20:19.367 --> 20:21.601
Did You Check
Your Pants?

20:21.601 --> 20:23.601
- I'm Wearing Them!
- Just Go In.

20:23.601 --> 20:26.234
Thank You.
Terribly Sorry 
About All That.

20:26.234 --> 20:27.601
That's Not Bad.

20:27.601 --> 20:29.534
With A Bit
Of Direction
From Me,

20:29.534 --> 20:31.667
You Could Land Yourself
A Walk-On Part Somewhere.

20:31.667 --> 20:32.801
Perhaps Off Broadway.

20:32.801 --> 20:36.767
 <I>( SINGING IN Italian )</I>

20:38.734 --> 20:40.534
She's Russian,
You Know.

20:40.534 --> 20:43.234
Only Russia Can Still
Produce Women Like That.

20:54.601 --> 20:55.968
Henry:
 <I>So There We Are.</I>

20:57.767 --> 21:00.200
Where Are We?

21:00.200 --> 21:01.567
Sorry?

21:01.567 --> 21:05.200
I Like To Say That
Sometimes Before Retiring.

21:07.767 --> 21:09.734
 <I>I'm About To Put In</I>
 <I>My Ear Plugs.</I>

21:09.734 --> 21:12.601
Any Final Thoughts,
Questions?

21:12.601 --> 21:15.133
Yes. Can We Go
To The Opera Again Soon?

21:15.133 --> 21:17.467
Why Not?
We Can Afford It.

21:17.467 --> 21:20.334
Oh, Henry,
One More Thing.

21:20.334 --> 21:24.033
I Never Got To Ask You,
How Did Your Evening

21:24.033 --> 21:25.901
With The Billionairess Go?

21:25.901 --> 21:27.667
With Vivian?
It Was Fine.

21:27.667 --> 21:30.067
Except She Stopped Breathing
For A Full Minute.

21:30.067 --> 21:32.601
But Then She Rallied.
She Always Does.

21:32.601 --> 21:34.234
How Old Is She?

21:34.234 --> 21:36.901
She's 92.

21:36.901 --> 21:38.801
- 92?!
- <I>Yes.</I>

21:38.801 --> 21:41.968
That's A Little Old
For A Girlfriend,

21:41.968 --> 21:43.167
Don't You Think?

21:43.167 --> 21:45.667
Unfortunately,
She's Not My Girlfriend.

21:45.667 --> 21:48.234
I'm Just One
Of 20 Sycophants, Really.

21:48.234 --> 21:50.234
 <I>For Years Now I've Been</I>
 <I>Her First Choice,</I>

21:50.234 --> 21:52.667
 <I>But I Could Be On The Outs</I>
 <I>At Any Minute.</I>

21:52.667 --> 21:56.667
Barry Barbarash Wants
Desperately To See Me Omitted.

21:56.667 --> 21:59.200
 <I>He's Scheming</I>
 <I>To Be Permanently Installed</I>

21:59.200 --> 22:02.234
As The Resident
Rosen Knight.

22:02.234 --> 22:03.901
What's A "Rosen Knight"?

22:03.901 --> 22:05.734
 <I>It's A Knight</I>
 <I>Who Brings Roses.</I>

22:05.734 --> 22:08.200
A <I>"Rosenkavalier."</I>
An Escort.

22:08.200 --> 22:10.133
Henry...

22:11.200 --> 22:12.434
Are You A Gigolo?

22:12.434 --> 22:14.200
Don't Be Disgusting.

22:14.200 --> 22:16.033
I Am An "Extra Man."

22:16.033 --> 22:19.334
Although I Would Argue
I'm So Much More Than "Extra."

22:19.334 --> 22:20.767
 <I>I'm Essential.</I>

22:20.767 --> 22:23.234
Do These Old Ladies
Pay You?

22:23.234 --> 22:24.968
Of Course Not,
Except In Pleasure--

22:24.968 --> 22:27.801
 <I>A Fine Meal,</I>

22:27.801 --> 22:29.367
 <I>Vintage Champagne...</I>

22:30.601 --> 22:32.400
 <I>An Orchestra Perhaps.</I>

22:33.968 --> 22:37.033
 <I>You See,</I>
 <I>Women Outlive Men,</I>

22:37.033 --> 22:38.701
 <I>So There's Always A Need</I>

22:38.701 --> 22:40.901
 <I>For An Extra Man</I>
 <I>At The Table.</I>

22:40.901 --> 22:43.934
 <I>It Maintains A Proper</I>
 <I>Seating Arrangement.</I>

22:43.934 --> 22:45.901
 <I>Boy-Girl, Boy-Girl.</I>

22:45.901 --> 22:47.467
 <I>But Don't Think</I>
 <I>For A Moment</I>

22:47.467 --> 22:50.033
 <I>That It's All Champagne</I>
 <I>And Stardust.</I>

22:50.033 --> 22:54.100
 <I>An Extra Man Must Be</I>
 <I>Extremely Vigilant,</I>

22:54.100 --> 22:56.067
 <I>Especially When Dancing.</I>

22:56.067 --> 22:59.167
 <I>That's Why Escorts Are</I>
 <I>Often Called Walkers.</I>

22:59.167 --> 23:02.868
 <I>I, However,</I>
 <I>Am No Mere Walker.</I>

23:02.868 --> 23:05.300
 <I>What I Bring Is</I>
 <I>The Complete Package--</I>

23:05.300 --> 23:08.801
Wit, Intelligence,

23:08.801 --> 23:11.234
 <I>An Uncommon</I>
Joie De Vivre.

23:11.234 --> 23:13.334
I Wish I Had
 <I>Joie De Vivre.</I>

23:13.334 --> 23:15.834
 <I>Then I Could</I>
 <I>Be Your Assistant.</I>

23:15.834 --> 23:17.334
You're Very Young.

23:17.334 --> 23:20.501
 <I>But Vivian Does Have</I>
 <I>A Rather Attractive Niece.</I>

23:20.501 --> 23:23.200
- She Might Like You.
- That Would Be Incredible.

23:23.200 --> 23:25.534
Are We Having
A Conversation?

23:25.534 --> 23:28.133
Yes, I'd Say So.

23:28.133 --> 23:29.467
Well, It Has To Stop.

23:29.467 --> 23:31.801
We Should Know As Little
About Each Other As Possible.

23:31.801 --> 23:34.234
 <I>Good Relationships</I>
 <I>Have This Foundation.</I>

23:34.234 --> 23:35.834
 <I>Now Good Night.</I>

23:38.901 --> 23:40.767
Good Night, Henry.

23:49.567 --> 23:51.067
( CLEARS THROAT )
Hi, Mary.

23:52.133 --> 23:53.434
Oh, Hi.

23:55.734 --> 23:58.300
I See You're Eating
