23:58.300 --> 24:00.167
 <I>Yeah, I'm Really Behind.</I>

24:00.167 --> 24:02.934
- What Did You Get?
- Zen Palate.

24:02.934 --> 24:06.334
Ah, Are You
A Vegetarian?

24:06.334 --> 24:07.601
- Vegan.
- Ah.

24:07.601 --> 24:09.801
I'm Really Active
In Animal Rights.

24:09.801 --> 24:13.100
Oh, I Wish
I Could Be Vegan,

24:13.100 --> 24:16.234
But I Really Like Eggs.

24:16.234 --> 24:19.701
Although I Do Try To Order
Only Free-Range Chicken.

24:19.701 --> 24:20.701
 <I>( ELEVATOR BELL RINGS )</I>

24:20.701 --> 24:24.000
So I Went To The Opera
Last Night.

24:24.000 --> 24:27.234
- That's Cool.
