24:27.234 --> 24:29.334
I'm Pretty
Opera Illiterate,
Sorry To Say.

24:29.334 --> 24:32.467
Well, Maybe I Could
Take You Some Time.

24:32.467 --> 24:34.667
I Know How
To Get In For Free.

24:36.067 --> 24:39.400
Or We Could Just Go
For A Drink Somewhere
One Night.

24:39.400 --> 24:42.200
Maybe Even This Weekend?

24:42.200 --> 24:44.667
Thanks, Louis,

24:44.667 --> 24:46.567
But I'm Going
Out Of Town This Weekend.

24:46.567 --> 24:47.968
- Oh.
- We're Protesting
The Building

24:47.968 --> 24:50.467
Of A Cement Plant
On The Hudson.

24:50.467 --> 24:54.100
Actually, This Guy
I Started Seeing
Is Taking Me.

24:54.100 --> 24:57.501
Maybe You And I Could
Grab Lunch Out Together
One Day.

24:58.934 --> 25:00.667
- Okay?
- Sure.

25:01.934 --> 25:03.534
Thank You.

25:15.100 --> 25:16.400
Eww.

25:16.400 --> 25:18.534
I'm Sorry.
I'm Sorry.

25:18.534 --> 25:19.701
Sorry.
I'm Sorry.

25:20.934 --> 25:22.901
- ( SCOFFS )
- Sorry. Sorry.

25:39.400 --> 25:41.367
Narrator:
 <I>Two Competing Fantasies</I>

25:41.367 --> 25:43.801
 <I>Co-Existed</I>
 <I>Within Louis Ives.</I>

25:43.801 --> 25:46.701
 <I>A Sort Of Bipolar</I>
 <I>Condition</I>

25:46.701 --> 25:49.400
 <I>That Wasn't </I>
 <I>Mood-Related</I>

25:49.400 --> 25:51.067
 <I>But Sex-Related.</I>

25:52.300 --> 25:53.968
 <I>On The One Hand,</I>

25:53.968 --> 25:55.968
 <I>He Longed</I>
 <I>To Be A Young Gentleman,</I>

25:55.968 --> 25:59.400
 <I>One Who Wears Ties</I>
 <I>And Enjoys The Opera.</I>

25:59.400 --> 26:03.300
 <I>But Sometimes He Yearned</I>
 <I>To Look In The Mirror</I>

26:03.300 --> 26:05.667
 <I>And See A Pretty Girl.</I>

26:05.667 --> 26:08.267
 <I>One Filled</I>
 <I>With Adoration And Love,</I>

26:08.267 --> 26:10.167
 <I>Smiling Back At Him.</I>

26:10.167 --> 26:11.834
 <I>( DOORBELL BUZZES )</I>

26:11.834 --> 26:13.167
 <I>For Some Reason,</I>

26:13.167 --> 26:15.033
 <I>He Believed</I>
 <I>The Woman In The Ad</I>

26:15.033 --> 26:17.067
 <I>Might Help Him</I>
 <I>With His Confusion.</I>

26:17.067 --> 26:19.734
Oh... Hello.

26:21.601 --> 26:22.901
Hello.

26:22.901 --> 26:24.634
Um, It's Okay.

26:24.634 --> 26:27.501
