26:29.968 --> 26:31.501
More Than Fine, I Mean.

26:31.501 --> 26:34.000
All Right.

26:34.000 --> 26:36.434
Well,
Come On In Then.

26:38.701 --> 26:40.234
So I'm Katherine,

26:40.234 --> 26:43.300
But You Can Call Me
Miss Hart.

26:43.300 --> 26:45.033
What Was Your Name Again,
Sweetheart?

26:45.033 --> 26:46.767
George.

26:46.767 --> 26:48.200
George.

26:48.200 --> 26:51.601
All Right, Then We Will
Call You Georgina,

26:51.601 --> 26:54.534
Unless You're Not Interested
In The Crossdressing Part.

26:54.534 --> 26:57.501
