That's Really
Why I Called.

26:57.501 --> 26:59.501
Have You Dressed Up A Lot?

26:59.501 --> 27:02.200
 <I>No, Hardly At All.</I>

27:02.200 --> 27:03.834
It's Weird.
I Don't Really Have

27:03.834 --> 27:06.033
Anyone I Can
Talk To About...

27:06.033 --> 27:07.868
This Urge.

27:07.868 --> 27:11.067
- <I>( TIMER CLICKING )</I>
- Well, You Can Talk To Me.

27:11.067 --> 27:13.000
All Right?
That's Why You're Here.

27:13.000 --> 27:16.000
You Tell Miss Hart
Everything.

27:16.000 --> 27:17.367
Here, Have A Seat.

27:17.367 --> 27:18.834
Okay.

27:18.834 --> 27:24.534
Well, I Think
It All Started

27:24.534 --> 27:26.234
When I Was A Little Boy.

27:26.234 --> 27:29.734
I Saw This Cartoon

27:29.734 --> 27:32.901
Where A Duck
Wearing A Tuxedo

27:32.901 --> 27:36.100
Was Transformed
Into A Beautiful Girl.

27:36.100 --> 27:39.100
 <I>Seeing That Stirred</I>
 <I>Something In Me.</I>

27:50.667 --> 27:52.734
Soon After,
I Discovered A Book.

27:54.334 --> 27:58.267
 <I>I Worried I Might Be Like</I>
 <I>The People Described In It.</I>

27:58.267 --> 28:01.300
Over The Years,
I've Had Very Few Lovers--

28:01.300 --> 28:03.400
And You're Lonely.

28:03.400 --> 28:05.367
And You Desire
The Company Of A Woman.

28:05.367 --> 28:07.133
And You Know What,

28:07.133 --> 28:10.267
That's As Good A Reason
