Okay.

28:27.934 --> 28:32.434
So The First Thing
We Have To Do

28:32.434 --> 28:34.701
Is Teach You
To Be Feminine.

28:36.200 --> 28:38.000
First, You're
Gonna Learn How To Sit.

28:38.000 --> 28:39.434
Go Ahead.

28:42.634 --> 28:44.801
No No No No.
Okay.

