 <I>Threw Rice With The Rest,</I>

01:43:18.701 --> 01:43:21.400
 <I>He Finally Understood</I>
 <I>Those Words</I>

01:43:21.400 --> 01:43:23.467
 <I>Of His Dear</I>
 <I>And Essential Friend</I>

